              <span class="author">
                <a href="/experts/paul-ratner">Paul Ratner</a>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="abstract">
              <p>
                 A new study finds that one of the world&#x27;s most popular painkillers affects the ability to empathize with the suffering of others.  
              </p>
            </div>
            
